text: A Strange Role (, and released in the US as Strange Masquerade) is a 1976 Hungarian drama movie directed by Pál Sándor and starring Margit Dajka, Irma Patkós, Carla Romanelli, Dezső Garas, Ildikó Pécsi, Mária Lázár, Ági Margittay. ==Other websites== * Category:1976 drama movies Category:Hungarian movies
title: A Strange Role
